Sentencas: Effect of preparation method for Pr0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (PSCF) on its electrochemical performance was investigated.
Titulo: Impact of synthesis technique on the structure and electrochemical characteristics of Pr0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ (PSCF) cathode material

Sentencas: Powder samples were synthesized by hexamethylenetetramine (HMTA) and EDTA-citric acid (EC) techniques, respectively.
Titulo: Impact of synthesis technique on the structure and electrochemical characteristics of Pr0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ (PSCF) cathode material

Sentencas: The particles synthesized by HMTA were smaller than those prepared by EC method as proved by TEM.
Titulo: Impact of synthesis technique on the structure and electrochemical characteristics of Pr0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ (PSCF) cathode material

Sentencas: X-ray photoelectron spectroscopy illuminated that more oxygen sites including oxygen vacancy on the surface of HMTA-derived PSCF exist than that of EC-derived PSCF.
Titulo: Impact of synthesis technique on the structure and electrochemical characteristics of Pr0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ (PSCF) cathode material

Sentencas: The area specific resistance (ASR) value of HMTA-derived PSCF cathode was as low as 0.454 Omega cm(2) at 600 degrees C, whereas the ASR value of EC-derived PSCF was 0.641 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Impact of synthesis technique on the structure and electrochemical characteristics of Pr0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ (PSCF) cathode material

Sentencas: The results in the present study demonstrated the advantages of the HMTA method in the synthesis of highly catalytic active PSCF oxide powder for SOFCs.
Titulo: Impact of synthesis technique on the structure and electrochemical characteristics of Pr0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ (PSCF) cathode material
